transcript:

Executive: Ji ji main India Mart se baat kar rahi hu sir.

Executive: Ji ji main India Mart se baat kar rahi hu.

Executive: Kya ji? Unko di. Maangi thi account manager ne jo account manager hai na mere.

Executive: Theek hai sir haan to abhi ye concern hai agar jaise hi ho jayega hum aapko bata denge fir.
Customer: Okay theek hai aap isi number pe bhi contact kar lijiyega baki.
